The paper deals with privacy concerns in the Internet of Things and cloud computing, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses the integration of privacy functionality into the development process of cloud-based services, which could be related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and cybernetics (cs.CY). Additionally, the paper addresses user acceptance of cloud-based services, which could be related to software engineering (cs.SE) and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC).
